    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const body = $json.body || $json;\nconst sectionId = body.section_id;\nconst input = body.input_json || {};\nconst context = body.plan_context || {};\nconst language = body.language || 'english';\nconst businessPlanId = body.business_plan_id;\n\nconst headings = language === 'french' ? `\n- Annexes\n- Références\n- Documents juridiques\n` : `\n- Appendix\n- References\n- Legal Documents\n`;\n\nconst prompt = `\nYou are writing a professional business plan section: Appendices.\nLanguage: ${language}\n\n## Company Context\n${context.company_presentation || 'Not provided'}\n\n## Financial Context\n${context.financial_plan || 'Not provided'}\n\n## Risk Context\n${context.risk_opportunity || 'Not provided'}\n\n## Appendix Information\n- Supporting Documents: ${input.appendix_docs || 'Not provided'}\n- References: ${input.references || 'Not provided'}\n- CVs Attached: ${input.cvs_attached || 'Not provided'}\n- Market Links: ${input.market_links || 'Not provided'}\n\nWrite a detailed Appendices section. Include these headings: ${headings}\n\nRules:\n- Minimum 300 words\n- Write in ${language}\nCRITICAL INSTRUCTION — OUTPUT FORMAT:\nYou MUST return your response in exactly this format. Any other format is invalid.\n\n=== SECTION_TEXT ===\n[Write your full detailed section here]\n=== MEMORY_SUMMARY ===\nDocuments Attached: [value]\nKey References: [value]\nCertifications: [value]\n`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    prompt,\n    sectionId: sectionId,\n    business_plan_id: businessPlanId,\n    section_name: 'appendices',\n    language,\n    input_json: input,\n  }\n}];"
      },
